aste on my server, not sure how it is on your server.  It's always been my feeling that haste > everything, I mean you do have to have decent AC but I think you do with that gear.<br><br>Guardian Pauldrons -- 1 group can hunt in the Hole till some IGS drop, you will just get mighty tired of rock golems first<br><br>Icebear Cloak -- 1 group should be able to hunt seahorses till you get the Ancient Seahorse cloak. If you happen to be on giant faction there's a quest cloak you can do with 12AC, some resists and HP, and 5 charges of sup camo.<br> <p><table border="1"><tr><td align ="left" width="40%"><font face="garamond, palatino" size="+1" >	<a href="http://www.geocities.com/valya_peregrinus" target="_blank"> <b> <u>Valya Peregrinus </u></b></a>,</font><br>39 Paladin<br>Melliasan Peregrinus, 14 Minstrel<br> <a href="http://www.geocities.com/the_elders_of_camelot"><u>The Elders</u></a><br>Morgan Le Fay, Dark Age of Camelot<br></td><td align ="left" width="40%"><font face="garamond, palatino" size="+1">	<a href="http://www.geocities.com/valya_w" target="_blank"> <b> <u>Valya Wanderfoot </u></b></a>, </font><br>59 Knight<br>Melliasan Sforzanda, 40 Bard<br><a href="http://www.the-elders.com"><u>The Elders</u></a><br>Mithaniel Marr, EverQuest</td></tr></table></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvalyawanderfoot.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Valya Wanderfoot</A> at: 12/25/01 8:49:25 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uiron299wind.showPublicProfile?language=EN>iron299wind</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/25/01 11:45:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13586.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: need equipment upgrade for 